<Verbatim PAsource="" >A police sergeant </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >has been charged with </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >two </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >counts </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >of rape</Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >, one at a police station. </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Paul Banfield, 32, </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >a Cambridgesbire officer, has also been charged with indecent assault, theft and burglary.
</New>

<New PAsource="" >The police station rape is alleged to have taken place at Parkside, Cambridge, </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >on </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >Oct </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >9</Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >, where Sgt Banfield, a former Metropolitan Police officer, was based. </New>
<New PAsource="" >The indecent assault and theft charges relate to incidents on the same day.
</New>

<New PAsource="" >A second count of rape and the burglary charge are both alleged to have taken place at Waterbeach, Cambs.
